Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.50,0:00:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.30,0:00:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.94,0:00:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.88,0:00:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.56,0:00:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.56,0:00:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.17,0:00:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.61,0:00:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.61,0:01:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.82,0:01:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.25,0:01:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.72,0:01:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.36,0:01:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.83,0:01:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.30,0:01:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.74,0:01:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代有好好教妳嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.74,0:01:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.44,0:02:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃了晚飯再回去嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.61,0:02:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…可是爺爺在等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.25,0:02:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.19,0:02:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.09,0:02:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦,惣一郎,不可以這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.89,0:02:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.16,0:02:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.00,0:02:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嬸嬸,惣一郎給我牽好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.57,0:02:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想牽惣一郎的繩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.24,0:02:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好是好,可是妳牽得來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.51,0:02:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.11,0:02:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,小心點喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.58,0:02:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,我們走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.92,0:02:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.62,0:02:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.16,0:02:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.04,0:03:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看,青椒,豬肉塊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.41,0:03:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像還忘了什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.18,0:03:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.82,0:03:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.16,0:03:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.83,0:03:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#27 惣一郎不見了?\N回憶是烤肉串的香味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.17,0:03:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回家路上小心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.38,0:03:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,惣一郎,再見囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.85,0:03:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.68,0:03:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嬸嬸,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.55,0:03:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代我向爸爸問好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.35,0:03:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.15,0:03:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心點喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.06,0:03:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.97,0:04:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.90,0:04:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這隻狗哪裡來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.47,0:04:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從串烤店一直跟到這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.31,0:04:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好髒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.97,0:04:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子大概很餓了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.31,0:04:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.68,0:04:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠叫小白?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.28,0:04:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦,因為牠是白色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.02,0:04:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙,這個不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.42,0:04:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,這是我要吃的\N不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.79,0:04:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白,住手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.76,0:04:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白,小白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.37,0:04:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.27,0:04:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.97,0:04:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,賢太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.65,0:04:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,小白是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.95,0:04:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.68,0:04:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.89,0:05:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,妳有東西要買,不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.72,0:05:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帶牠去散步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.09,0:05:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.63,0:05:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託你囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.21,0:05:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時在某些小事上\N會感受到時光的流逝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.62,0:05:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轉眼間發現自己已經變成\N這個城鎮的居民了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.03,0:05:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.46,0:05:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的豬肉怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.07,0:05:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在豬肉在大減價喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.93,0:05:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊,那我得趕快去買
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.80,0:05:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,那我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.67,0:05:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.97,0:05:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.91,0:05:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小綾,走路要看路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.25,0:06:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當初我自己決定\N踏進一刻館的大門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.79,0:06:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎已經是很久以前的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.98,0:06:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我嚐嚐看…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.01,0:06:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.58,0:06:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎有沒有回來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.85,0:06:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的,牠不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.76,0:06:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠不見了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.73,0:06:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我們正要過平交道的時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.45,0:07:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.52,0:07:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電車過後,我雖然馬上回去找牠…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.63,0:07:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.36,0:07:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠一定又被烤肉串給吸引走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.70,0:07:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再去找找看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.76,0:07:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心,牠馬上就會回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.10,0:07:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.03,0:07:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的不用擔心啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.70,0:07:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎很能幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.18,0:07:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦,惣一郎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.38,0:07:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下落不明是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.05,0:07:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一找不到,我該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.52,0:07:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會有事的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.69,0:07:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠應該擁有歸巢本能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.16,0:07:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.50,0:07:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛\N惣一郎一向很厚臉皮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.73,0:08:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是,歸巢本能是什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.87,0:08:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.34,0:08:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.41,0:08:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辭典
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.78,0:08:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.48,0:08:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拿辭典給我幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.71,0:08:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我沒有自信\N能簡單明瞭地解釋給妳聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.23,0:09:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.76,0:09:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不需要逃走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.11,0:09:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小朋友,借問一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.24,0:09:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.88,0:09:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有看到一隻這麼大\N白色的,笨笨的狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.95,0:09:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.25,0:09:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛,不知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.38,0:09:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.32,0:10:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.86,0:10:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(串烤)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.31,0:10:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.11,0:10:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.61,0:10:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.60,0:10:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.71,0:10:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他很在意惣一郎走失的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.41,0:11:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(尋狗啟事像個糟老頭的白狗\N連絡地點一刻館)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.82,0:11:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記住喔,你叫小白,小白喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.12,0:11:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.22,0:11:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,吃飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.86,0:11:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.05,0:11:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過說真的\N惣一郎真的像個糟老頭嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.63,0:11:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有著歷盡風霜的臉龐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.43,0:11:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,枯竭又有味道的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.94,0:12:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說\N都不是年輕的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.11,0:12:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎也真傻,就是那麼愛吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.25,0:12:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.62,0:12:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.79,0:12:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼危險?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.99,0:12:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.70,0:12:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我一點什麼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.10,0:12:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.07,0:13:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你太無情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.07,0:13:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得向窮學生敲詐\N才是極端沒人性的行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.04,0:13:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在擔心惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.88,0:13:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這跟牠有什麼關係?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.45,0:13:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要知道,這已經是第五天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.12,0:13:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有聽過這句俗話嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.15,0:13:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狗是養了三天的女孩\N被外國人帶走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.53,0:13:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狗是不會忘記\N被養了三天的思情的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.83,0:13:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說如果啦\N如果牠被別人家撿走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.93,0:13:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定牠就會拋棄管理員\N在別人家住下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.54,0:13:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很危險吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.17,0:13:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.64,0:13:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那牠要怎麼回報\N管理員長期以來對牠的照顧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.85,0:13:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要知道,牠是一條狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.29,0:13:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.30,0:14:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這條狗怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.86,0:14:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得蠻像的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.63,0:14:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得差不多該死心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.54,0:14:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫管理員委屈一下\N換這條狗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.67,0:14:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行不通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.04,0:14:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.27,0:14:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員在找的不是一條白狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.01,0:14:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.72,0:15:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人能夠代替的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.16,0:15:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白狗,短腿,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.43,0:15:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美到處拜託朋友和客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.90,0:15:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才找到這條狗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.80,0:15:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法,把這條狗還回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.87,0:15:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說或許有點不吉利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.08,0:15:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去環保局之類的地方\N找找看比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.45,0:15:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠不在環保局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.61,0:15:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,順便再告訴你\N也沒有接到出車禍的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.85,0:15:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著再告訴你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.65,0:15:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是要賣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.99,0:15:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒說完耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.02,0:15:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,到底跑到哪裡去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.60,0:15:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.84,0:15:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.54,0:15:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,我看過\N一條白色的大狗對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.44,0:15:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛茸茸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.54,0:15:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛很長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.85,0:15:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耳朵塌塌的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.98,0:16:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛像疙瘩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胖胖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.05,0:16:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腿很短
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.55,0:16:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樸素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.85,0:16:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點土土的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.86,0:16:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對,它在洋子家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.40,0:16:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們等一下喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.00,0:16:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.17,0:16:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,終於找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.20,0:16:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找得好辛苦喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.94,0:17:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的很努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.85,0:17:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好緊張喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.99,0:17:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別…別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.69,0:17:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是弄錯狗了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.59,0:17:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集那麼多缺點於一身的狗\N除了惣一郎之外沒有別隻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.50,0:17:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錯不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.80,0:17:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…你說得對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.44,0:17:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洋子,妳要去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.84,0:17:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出去一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.51,0:17:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.81,0:17:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你要去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.84,0:17:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想去通知管理員啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.58,0:17:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋,你要放我一個人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.65,0:17:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,這隻狗對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.62,0:17:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.43,0:17:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.19,0:18:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.42,0:18:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後妳打算怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.29,0:19:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.77,0:19:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.57,0:19:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在找惣一郎嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.17,0:19:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎已經不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.61,0:19:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經…不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.29,0:19:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.22,0:19:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.06,0:20:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走,我們再去找找看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.16,0:20:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去那邊找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.50,0:20:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.55,0:20:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的找不到了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涅夫卡德薩比較好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.38,0:20:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭西斯比較好啦\N不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.59,0:20:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們不要吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.62,0:20:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種又髒又笨的狗\N叫牠“阿呆”最適合了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.66,0:20:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就決定叫阿呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.86,0:20:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,阿呆,吃飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.46,0:21:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.74,0:21:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.54,0:22:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.88,0:22:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五…五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.85,0:22:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.55,0:22:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.70,0:23:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.07,0:23:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟五代去參加\N賢太郎的運動會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.34,0:23:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過其實賢太郎最想跟爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.51,0:24:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!爸爸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.58,0:24:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.41,0:24:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「響子也嚇一跳\N我是賢太郎的爸爸」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.19,0:24:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來一之瀨太太是有老公的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.51,0:24:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天在陌生的城市下了一場陣雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.58,0:24:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳非常在意淋溼的高跟鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.39,0:24:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從前妳用那隱藏著\N稚氣的側臉和我交談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.46,0:24:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說的話語至今仍能想起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.60,0:25:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就彷佛\N置身電影中的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.31,0:25:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳輕聲細語地說著\N安靜的最後一幕
